[SN]TITLE[SN]
Euro 2016: Every game is a cup final - Wales manager Chris Coleman

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Manager Chris Coleman says Wales will be the underdogs against England in Thursday's Euro 2016 match.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Media playback is not supported on this device
Wales are top of Group B after their a 2-1 win over Slovakia in their opening game on Saturday.
"Thursday is like a cup final," Coleman told BBC Wales Sport. "Every game to us is a final.
"It's a great opportunity for us and a great experience."
